virus

Class VirusGroupManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • virus.VirusGroupManager

  • public class VirusGroupManager
extends java.lang.Object
    Manages the virus groups

    knows which group is to be updated, controls splitting and merging groups, keeps tracks ono all the groups in a hash map and has another array list to access the keys
